@startuml
participant User
participant LogIn
participant API
participant Vuex
participant Router
participant LocalStorage

User -> LogIn : Fill username and password
User -> LogIn : Click "Login"
LogIn -> API : POST /login with credentials
API -> LogIn : Respond with token and user data (or error)
alt Successful login
    LogIn -> LocalStorage : Store username and JWT token
    LogIn -> Vuex : setUser(user)
    alt First login
        LogIn -> Router : Navigate to welcomePage
    else Admin user
        LogIn -> Router : Navigate to adminDashboard
    else Regular user
        LogIn -> Router : Navigate to userOptionsPage
    end
else Login failed
    LogIn -> LogIn : Set snackbarMessage ("Invalid credentials")
    LogIn -> LogIn : Show snackbar
end
@enduml
